/mysterio-to-face-reigns-on-smackdown|title=Mysterio to face Reigns in a Hell in a Cell Match on SmackDown tomorrow night|date= 2021-06-17|author=WWE.com Staff|work=[[WWE|WWE]]|access-date= 2021-06-17|language=en}}</ref> 瑞恩斯成為勝利者。<ref name="SmackDown06182021">{{cite web|last1=Powell|first1=Jason|title=6/18 WWE Friday Night Smackdown results: Powell’s review of Roman Reigns vs. Rey Mysterio in a Hell in a Cell match for the WWE Universal Championship, Big E and Kevin Owens vs. Apollo Crews and Commander Azeez, Shinsuke Nakamura vs. King Corbin in a battle for the crown, Angelo Dawkins vs. Otis|url=https://prowrestling.net/site/2021/06/18/6-18-wwe-friday-night-smackdown-results-powells-review-of-roman-reigns-vs-rey-mysterio-in-a-hell-in-a-cell-match-for-the-wwe-universal-championship-big-e-and-kevin-owens-vs-apollo-crews-and-comm/|work=Pro Wrestling Dot Net|date= 2021-06-18|access-date= 2021-06-19|language=en}}</ref> 在6月25日的SmackDown中，瑞恩斯在談到他對密斯特里歐的勝利時遭到回歸的[[Edge_(摔角手)|Edge]]攻擊。<ref name="SmackDown06252021">{{cite web |last1=Powell |first1=Jason |title=6/25 WWE Friday Night Smackdown results: Powell's review of Roman Reigns' victory celebration, Apollo Crews vs. Big E in a Money in the Bank qualifier, Bianca Belair and Cesaro vs. Bayley and Seth Rollins in a mixed tag match |url=https://prowrestling.net/site/2021/06/25/6-25-wwe-friday-night-smackdown-results-powells-review-of-roman-reigns-victory-celebration-apollo-crews-vs-big-e-in-a-money-in-the-bank-qualifier-bianca-belair-and-cesaro-vs-bayley-and-seth-r/ |website=Pro Wrestling Dot Net |date= 2021-06-25 |access-date= 2021-06-26|language=en}}</ref> 導致兩人在公事包大戰進行冠軍賽，在賽特·羅林斯的幫助下，瑞恩斯持續衛冕頭銜。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Clapp|first=John|title=Universal Champion Roman Reigns def. Edge; John Cena returns to stand toe-to-toe with Reigns|url=https://www.wwe.com/shows/moneyinthebank/07-18-2021/roman-reigns-vs-edge-results|work=[[WWE|WWE]]|date= 2021-07-18|access-date= 2021-07-18|language=en}}</ref> 比賽結束後，瑞恩斯遇到回歸的[[約翰·希南|約翰·希南]]。在接下來的幾